Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.data.base.api.persistence.data

Annotation Type PersistenceUnit


  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(TYPE)
public @interface PersistenceUnit
    This annotation is designed to mark some subclass of PersistenceManagerFactorySupplier.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element Description
      java.lang.String name
      Name of a target persistence-unit.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
      org.datanucleus.metadata.TransactionType transactionType
      Defines transaction type for the persistence-unit.
      java.lang.String uri
      Root URI of the unit.

    • Element Detail
